{"tid":733424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[揮手區]支持特首林鄭帶領全港上下與全中國共同抗美體現血濃於水","createTime":"2018-07-07T17:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T08:15:27.000Z","uid":16562,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13e48209d13f4c13560c756c3a9769a6a5efd67a","tid":733424,"uid":16562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"如今美帝惡霸態度盡現去欺壓當今和平崛起既中國!<br />\n係呢個艱難既日子就係展現出香港人愛國心既最好時侯!<br />\n<br />\n希望特首林鄭月娥帶頭宣佈香港將與祖國站在同一陣線上<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共同抗美</span><br />\n從而令全港市民真心感受到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家都係中國人</span>同埋係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">血濃於水</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n起來！不願做奴隸的人們！把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"95a8b3b19ff3b85acac8f515a5a55975a68a337e","tid":733424,"uid":16562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美帝發動貿易戰擺到明挑中國機!支持特首宣佈香港收美國關稅!</span>"},{"pid":"063ce72affd50a28112e1c8727c728de3e30fff4","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"640ee0056b204c7d9d1e7eb5ee8b051cc7109871","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e23db5549bfc7a7f57b773c348302e37df5fa1c3","tid":733424,"uid":22928,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"063ce72affd50a28112e1c8727c728de3e30fff4","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:42:50.000Z","msg":"樓豬個銀包可能全部係淫民弊呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588dac41f310b6d9ff24c86953086b565adbb354","tid":733424,"uid":16562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"063ce72affd50a28112e1c8727c728de3e30fff4","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"香港政府之前日日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">血濃於水</span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家都係中國人</span><br />\n<br />\n所以香港政府應該要帶頭展現呢種精神!"},{"pid":"aba08314c9901a8e1a2185e2c7022c4477cb1e9e","tid":733424,"uid":16562,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"640ee0056b204c7d9d1e7eb5ee8b051cc7109871","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:45:42.000Z","msg":"咁當然要加埋香港 因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港都係中國一部份</span>"},{"pid":"559b18c95680210253e102f4d9e13ff433a2c7c1","tid":733424,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:58:05.000Z","msg":"人民幣開始下跌，變癈紙。 今日有四個大陸閪食晚飯話身上無港幣，但有人民幣問個店主收唔收...點知店主答應話1對1。 班大陸閪即場嚇到好驚青。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6672c8c8b714e2168712d8275b0b5045aa76d936","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"247a193319af80c8c2a4b8b63be7ad184c6a618d","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aca3b3e342b8989102b5685ade3e14ecbf8da735","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b986fc4478f89c8a7cf740b7845fe21f6b965cc3","tid":733424,"uid":16562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"247a193319af80c8c2a4b8b63be7ad184c6a618d","tid":733424,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有好多樓係手寜願想保住個市都唔做漢奸走狗賣國賊?</span>"},{"pid":"fa8ac6d3e783407e0122c887ee3e43ac5703